\begin{align}4+2x\gt 7&\iff 4+2x-4\gt 7-4\\&\iff 2x\gt 3\\&\iff 2x/2\gt 3/2\ \ (\because 2\gt 0)\\&\iff x\gt 3/2=1.5.\end{align}
a\gt 0
b\gt c\iff b/a\gt c/a.
\require{cancel}\begin{align} 4+2x\gt 7&\overset{\mathbf{Pr. 1}}{\iff} 4+2x\color{red}{-4}\gt 7\color{red}{-4}\\\,\\ & \iff 2x \gt 3 \\ \,\\ & \overset{\mathbf{Pr. 2}}{\iff}2x\cdot\dfrac12 \gt 3\dfrac 12 \\ \, \\ & \iff x\gt 3/2=1.5 \end{align}
